wiki.summary: “Designer” is one of Lil Pump’s most lyrical tracks to date. The “Gucci Gang” rapper flaunts his success and riches in the faces of his haters. The beat samples Shawty Lo’s classic anthem “I’m Da Man” (which Zay also recently sampled just a few years back). Lil Pump decided to surprise his fans and release this track as an early Christmas gift. Read more on Last.fm.
